    "intro": "Application is where Observation and Interpretation become obedience. Each question is paired with a specific movement of the chapter. Read it slowly, answer it honestly, and refuse to generalize — name the specific relationship, the specific temptation, the specific area of prosperity that has produced forgetfulness. The text addresses you in the second person because the questions belong to your actual life.",
